# Day06

## Part 1
``` PowerShell
$PI = ""

for($i=0;$i -lt $pi.length;$i++){

    $arr  = @()
    $arr += $pi[$i]
    $arr += $pi[$i+1]
    $arr += $pi[$i+2]
    $arr += $pi[$i+3]
    
    $dupe = $arr | group | where {$_.Count -gt 1}
    
    if(-not($dupe)){
        $i + 4
        break
    }
}
```

## Part 2
``` PowerShell
$PI = ""
for($i=0;$i -lt $pi.length;$i++){

    $arr  = @()
    for ($c = 0; $c -lt 15; $c++)    { 
        $arr += $pi[$i+$c]   
    }
    
    $dupe = $arr | group | where {$_.Count -gt 1}
    
    if(-not($dupe)){
        $i + 14
        break
    }
}
```
